---
/* CONTRACT: Internal mock custom chat shell prototype for feasibility; no backend/agent integration. */
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Section from "../../../components/layout/Section.astro";
import Footer from "../../../components/nav/Footer.astro";

Astro.response.headers.set("X-Robots-Tag", "noindex, follow");
---

<BaseLayout title="VOX – Sandbox: Chat Shell (intern)" currentPath="/no/sandbox/chat-shell">
  <meta slot="head" name="robots" content="noindex,follow" />

  <main class="pb-8 sm:pb-10">
    <Section class="!pt-4 !pb-8 sm:!pb-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.03em] text-balance sm:text-4xl">
          Chat shell prototype (intern)
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">
          Visual feasibility-spike for VOX-owned chat shell. Static mock only in this phase.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <Section tone="band" class="!py-7 sm:!py-9">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[920px]">
        <div
          class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] border border-[rgb(var(--border))/0.2] bg-[rgb(var(--surface-elevated))/0.78] shadow-[var(--shadow-md)] backdrop-blur-md"
        >
          <div class="border-b border-[rgb(var(--border))/0.16] bg-[rgb(var(--surface-subtle))/0.72] px-4 py-3 sm:px-5">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">VOX · Hørehjelpen</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--text))]">Custom shell mock</p>
          </div>

          <div class="max-h-[min(60vh,560px)] overflow-y-auto px-3 py-4 sm:px-5 sm:py-6">
            <div class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-3xl flex-col gap-2.5 sm:gap-3">
              <div class="max-w-[88%] rounded-[1rem] rounded-bl-md bg-[rgb(var(--surface-subtle))/0.95] px-3.5 py-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--text-secondary))] sm:max-w-[82%] sm:px-4">
                Hei! Beskriv kort hva som er vanskelig med høreapparatet akkurat nå, så tar vi ett steg om gangen.
              </div>

              <div class="ml-auto max-w-[88%] rounded-[1rem] rounded-br-md bg-[rgb(var(--surface))/0.98] px-3.5 py-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--text))] shadow-[var(--shadow-sm)] ring-1 ring-[rgb(var(--border))/0.18] sm:max-w-[82%] sm:px-4">
                Jeg mister ofte lyden når jeg bytter mellom mobil og TV.
              </div>

              <div class="max-w-[88%] rounded-[1rem] rounded-bl-md bg-[rgb(var(--surface-subtle))/0.95] px-3.5 py-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--text-secondary))] sm:max-w-[82%] sm:px-4">
                Skjønner. Start med å bekrefte at høreapparatet er aktivt parret til riktig enhet nå, så tar vi byttet stegvis.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 bottom-[98px] h-20 bg-gradient-to-t from-[rgb(var(--surface-elevated))/0.94] via-[rgb(var(--surface-elevated))/0.62] to-transparent"></div>

          <div class="sticky bottom-0 bg-[rgb(var(--surface-elevated))/0.96] px-3 pb-3.5 pt-2.5 backdrop-blur-md sm:px-5 sm:pb-5 sm:pt-3">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
              <label for="chat-shell-input" class="sr-only">Skriv melding</label>
              <div class="flex items-end gap-1.5 rounded-[1rem] bg-[rgb(var(--surface))/0.98] px-2 py-2.5 shadow-[var(--shadow-sm)] ring-1 ring-[rgb(var(--border))/0.18] sm:gap-2 sm:p-2.5">
                <textarea
                  id="chat-shell-input"
                  rows="1"
                  placeholder="Skriv melding…"
                  class="min-h-[54px] w-full resize-none rounded-[0.85rem] bg-transparent px-2.5 py-2.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[rgb(var(--text))] placeholder:text-[rgb(var(--muted))] focus:outline-none sm:min-h-[56px] sm:px-3 sm:py-3"
                ></textarea>
                <button
                  type="button"
                  class="inline-flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-[0.8rem] bg-[rgb(var(--primary))/0.14] text-[rgb(var(--primary))] shadow-[0_6px_14px_-10px_rgb(var(--primary)/0.65)] transition-colors hover:bg-[rgb(var(--primary))/0.2] focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-[rgb(var(--focus-ring))/0.45] focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-[rgb(var(--surface))] sm:h-11 sm:w-11"
                  aria-label="Send melding"
                >
                  <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
